1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 11:1473, relative to the Assessors' Retirement Fund; to provide relative to
3 correction of administrative errors; to provide for calculation of interest; to provide
4 for an effective date; and to provide for related matters.
5 Notice of intention to introduce this Act has been published
6 as provided by Article X, Section 29(C) of the Constitution
